item.title: CVE-2022-43413|2024-08-03T13:32:57.372Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20job%20import%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Job Import Plugin 3.5 and earlier does not perform a permission check in an HTTP endpoint, allowing attackers with Overall/Read permission to enumerate credentials IDs of credentials stored in Jenkins.
